    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People designated by title "kahn," supreme rulers over certain Turkish, Tartar, and Mongol tribes, as well as emperors of China, during the Middle Ages; successors of Chingīz Khan.</Note_Text>
